    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with no signs of wear on the upholstery and every feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle in showroom-quality state.",
